# Image Captioning AI

## Description
This project is a cloud-based Image Captioning AI that generates natural-language descriptions for any image. Fully free to run using Google Colab and Gradio, with an optional FastAPI backend for deployment.

## Features
- Uses Hugging Face BLIP model
- Generates captions for uploaded images
- Interactive Gradio UI with free public link
- Optional backend API (FastAPI) for cloud deployment

## Setup

Google Colab (Recommended)
1. Open `main.ipynb` in Google Colab.
2. Run all cells.
3. Use the Gradio interface to upload images and get captions.

